Package userinterface

Class DocumentCell

java.lang.Object
userinterface.Frame
userinterface.DocumentCell
Direct Known Subclasses:
UIButton, UIForm, UITable, UITextField, UITextHyperlink, UITextInputField
public class DocumentCell
extends Frame
A class to represent individual UI elements that need to be rendered.

      id - : The id of the click
      x - : The x coordinate of the click
      y - : The y coordinate of the click
      clickCount - : The number of clicks that occured.
      button - : Which mouse button was clicked.
      modifier - : Extra control key that was held during the click.
      Returns:
      ReturnMessage(ReturnMessage.Type.Empty): a ReturnMessage which contains the empty string "".
